text: Jeong Jae-won (born 9 June 1969) is a South Korean rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. He attended Korea National Sport University. He also competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1989 Summer Universiade. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of South Korea Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Korea National Sport University alumni
